END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Authority: 36 U.S.C. 129\nReason: Federal law requests that the U.S. flag be displayed at half-staff from sunrise to sunset on National Pearl Harbor Remembrance Day. The observance honors the service members and civilians who died in the December 7\, 1941 attack and remembers the sacrifice that drew the nation into World War II.\nSource: https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title36-section129&num=0&edition=prelim
DTEND:20271207T214724Z
DTSTART:20271207T121430Z
SUMMARY:National Pearl Harbor Remembrance Day
UID:9d7729cfb430e54c38fcefb433d2b808a6127db880f7f7519d2b4be01e34491c
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Authority: Missouri Governor\nReason: May 14\, 2026 You can access the proclamation here . State government departments are responsible for distributing this information throughout your department for compliance with this order. Sincerely\, OA-FMDC Governor Kehoe Proclaims May 11-17\, 2026\, to be Peace Officers Memorial Week WHEREAS \, Missouri's peace officers bravely and altruistically work toward securing the safety and welfare of their fellow citizens\; and WHEREAS \, the 15th of May is designated as Missouri's Peace Officers Memorial\nSource: https://oa.mo.gov/facilities/facilities-operations/flag-display/flag-notifications
DTEND:20260516T011429Z
DTSTART:20260515T105822Z
SUMMARY:Governor Mike Kehoe has ordered that the flag of the United States and the flag of Missouri be flown at half-staff over the State Capitol and at all government offices throughout Missouri on Friday\, May 15\, 2026\, from sunrise to sunset\, in honor of Peace Officers Memorial Day.
UID:7a35dadb9f6e247961285830b3b23879b7c68e687dd251b4e6fcc4ec040278d4
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Authority: US President\nReason: President Donald Trump ordered all American flags throughout the United States lowered to half-staff in honor of the life and achievements of Senator Lindsey Graham. Flags are to remain lowered until 6 p.m. on Saturday\, July 18\, 2026.\nSource: https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/2026/07/death-of-senator-lindsey-graham/
DTEND:20260719T010000Z
DTSTART:20260713T003000Z
SUMMARY:President Trump orders flags to half-staff in honor of Senator Lindsey Graham
UID:8842f3fab76883193feaecee23509560f996c1898d75526a55e76965ea30a66e
END:VEVENT
